00:13:48,471 --> 00:13:52,492
hey, we told you you could have this much space, but we've changed it at the last minute,

233
00:13:52,772 --> 00:13:59,133
we found that we can get away with a 20 by 6 foot track space and put four players concurrently tracked within that.

234
00:13:59,653 --> 00:14:02,874
And that helps us keep our footprint down and that keeps venues pretty happy.

235
00:14:02,894 --> 00:14:08,255
Yeah, and that's in a single Vive lighthouse track space, which is pretty convenient.

236
00:14:11,253 --> 00:14:14,954
So also, it's important to remember that every venue has different physical setups,

237
00:14:15,014 --> 00:14:17,235
and so you're going to have to set up your tracking in different ways.

